          "message": { "text": "The Orchestrator's context window may be tampered with by an attacker who controls any upstream data source — the Knowledge Base, Inter-Agent Channel, or MCP Tool Server responses.", "markdown": "Validate the integrity of all context sources before injecting into the Orchestrator's context window. Apply content-level hashing to retrieved documents at KB read time." },
