          "message": { "text": "The Specialist Agent's operational context may be tampered with by injecting adversarial content into the Delegated Task message via the Inter-Agent Communication Channel.", "markdown": "Validate and sanitize all task payloads received by the Specialist Agent before execution. Apply message integrity verification (HMAC or digital signature) on every received delegation message." },
