          "message": { "text": "Messages transiting the Inter-Agent Communication Channel may be modified in transit by a process with access to the channel's message queue, enabling agent-in-the-middle attacks.", "markdown": "Apply end-to-end message integrity protection (digital signatures) at the channel layer. Use message sequence numbers and monotonic counters to detect dropped or reordered messages." },
