          "message": { "text": "Tool call request parameters supplied by agent LLM outputs may be tampered with if the Tool Server does not validate them against an explicit allowlist, enabling injection of malicious arguments.", "markdown": "Implement strict parameter validation on all JSON-RPC tool invocations. Apply parameter-level allowlisting before tool dispatch." },
