          "message": { "text": "The Knowledge Base corpus may be tampered with (poisoned) by an attacker who gains write access, corrupting the Orchestrator's retrieved context at scale.", "markdown": "Implement write access controls on the Knowledge Base with least-privilege service accounts. Apply document-level integrity checks at write time; verify at retrieval time." },
